[27/06/2018 12:42:59] <font color="#ffff00">Gracias.</font>
[27/06/2018 12:43:01] <font color="#ffff00">Vaya...</font>
[27/06/2018 12:43:04] <font color="#ffff00">Oh... Disculpe.</font>
